## 5. QueryDSL Projection 최적화

Entity 전체가 아닌 필요한 컬럼만 Projection으로 조회합니다.

**Before (Entity 전체 조회):**

```kotlin
// 모든 컬럼을 SELECT하여 불필요한 데이터 전송
val candidates: List<CallMatchingEntity> =
    matchingRepository.findByStatus(MatchingStatus.WAITING.value)
```

**After (Projection DTO):**

```kotlin
// MatchCandidateDto.kt
@QueryProjection // Q클래스 자동 생성
data class MatchCandidateDto(
    val userId: String,
    val waitingSince: LocalDateTime,
    val gender: Int,
    val ageGroup: Int,
    val region: String?,
    val interestTags: String?,
)

// Repository 구현
override fun findWaitingByPreference(
    gender: Int,
    ageGroup: Int,
    excludeUserId: String,
): List<MatchCandidateDto> {
    val matching = QCallMatchingEntity.callMatchingEntity
    val profile = QProfileEntity.profileEntity

    return queryFactory
        .select(
            QMatchCandidateDto(
                matching.userId,
                matching.createdAt,
                profile.gender,
                profile.ageGroup,
                profile.region,
                profile.interestTags,
            )
        )
        .from(matching)
        .innerJoin(profile).on(
            matching.userId.eq(profile.userId)
                .and(profile.gender.eq(gender).or(gender.eq(-1)))
                .and(profile.ageGroup.eq(ageGroup).or(ageGroup.eq(-1)))
        )
        .where(
            matching.status.eq(MatchingStatus.WAITING.value),
            matching.userId.ne(excludeUserId),
            matching.deletedAt.isNull,
        )
        .orderBy(matching.createdAt.asc())
        .limit(20)
        .fetch()
}
```

